                -=[ Appraisal ]=-

     	     Topic: Appraisal

	     Usage: appraise <item>
	  Synopsis: The appraisal ability is two fold:

			1) It enables someone to know the true worth of an item,
			thereby gaining a better deal in transactions for buying
			and selling items.

			2) It enables someone to assess the approximate value.

			The higher this statistic, the more reliable the bargaining
			and information gained from assessment.
	  

  Related Topics: None

